anisotime

クラス Phase

  • java.lang.Object
    • anisotime.Phase

  • public class Phase
extends java.lang.Object

    Phase name.

    This class is immutable.

    Waveform is now digitalized. Waveform is divided into parts. each part has up or downgoing, P or S and the partition in which waveform exists. PdiffXX and SdiffXX can be used. XX is positive double XX is diffractionAngle

    作成者:
    kensuke
